!              THIS SUBROUTINE, THERE WILL
!              BE NO CORRESPONDANCE BETWEEN
!              Y AND D (DUE TO THE PACKING OF
!              THE RETAINED ELEMENTS IN Y)
!              AFTER APPLICATION OF THIS SUBROUTINE.
